@maggot_corps: The NBA finals are played in max. 7 games (the best of 7 games). The games are played so: the first 2 games at the best team (between those two) in the regular season, the next 3 games at the opponent (the third if necessary) and the last 2 games (if necessary) again at the best team. Therefore it were 3 games Heat vs. Dallas.
